com.palantir.giraffe.command.interactive

Class OrderedResponseProvider<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.palantir.giraffe.command.interactive.AbstractResponseProvider<T>
      • com.palantir.giraffe.command.interactive.OrderedResponseProvider<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the response
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResponseProvider<T>

    public final class OrderedResponseProvider<T>
extends AbstractResponseProvider<T>
    An implementation of AbstractResponseProvider that matches <prompt, response> pairs sequentially. This means that if A and B are <prompt, response> pairs and A precedes B, the prompt for B will not be matched until the prompt for A is first matched. Moreover, each <prompt, response> pair will only ever be matched (and subsequently respond) only once.
